snippet.title: Soda Story - Brewing Tycoon - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Soda Story - Brewing Tycoon New in remastered / upscaled 4K UHD and 60 FPS

Soda Story - Brewing Tycoon is an adventurous casual management game in which you take on the challenge of running a Soda brewing operation. All while participating in the current season of the hit reality TV show “Prisoneers.”

TITLE: Soda Story - Brewing Tycoon
GENRE: Simulation
DEVELOPER: Upper Class Walrus
PUBLISHER: Upper Class Walrus
RELEASE DATE: Q3 2022

Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1088750/Soda_Story__Brewing_Tycoon/
